Laurent Blanc vacates his job as manager of the France national football team following his team's exit from the tournament. (BBC) (ESPN)Bundesliga football club Hoffenheim fires head coach Markus Babbel after the 1–4 loss to Werder Bremen in the 2012–13 season game. (Goal.com)Mano Menezes has left his post as Brazil national football team coach two days after winning the 2012 Superclásico de las Américas against Argentina on penalties, and just 19 months before the 2014 FIFA World Cup in Brazil. (Goal.com)